Global Chlorella Powder Market Insights
Chlorella Powder Market size was valued at USD 0.86 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.77 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Chlorella Powder Market Overview
The global Chlorella powder market is anticipated to grow significantly due to the increasing consumer awareness regarding the health benefits associated with Chlorella supplementation. As of 2024, the market value is estimated at USD 4.8 billion and is expected to register a healthy compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 8.5% over the forecast period, 2025-2030. This growth can be attributed to the rising demand for plant-based protein sources, detoxification properties, and immune-boosting benefits offered by Chlorella powder. The shift towards organic, non-GMO, and sustainable nutritional products further supports this market expansion.

